{"tid":1812401,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Pixel 3a XL 銷售欠佳   後續型號慘被 Google 腰斬","createTime":"2020-01-05T12:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T02:14:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7ced0d93a6418997de975f9c0ce308222511dae3","tid":1812401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"上星期版主虎仔分享過 Pixel 4a 的渲染圖，可能會在今年 5 月舉行的 Google I/O 發表，不過對於喜歡大屏幕的網友來說，今年可能會失望，因為最新消息指 Google 並沒有推出 Pixel 4a XL 的打算，只會推出一款中階 Pixel 4a。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-01/04/214882/uniqlo_1_c3d54e65b2161ffaa01c91baf32d95a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-01%2F04%2F214882%2Funiqlo_1_c3d54e65b2161ffaa01c91baf32d95a8.jpg&h=065284cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYouTuber Dave Lee 昨日上載了宣稱是 Pixel 4a 的機身設計渲染圖影片，他表示 Google 今年將不會推出 XL 型號，原因是去年上市的 Pixel 3a XL 銷情欠佳，消費者傾向購買屏幕尺寸較細的 Pixel 3a。Google 認為 Pixel 3a 屬市場上少有的細屏幕，但 Pixel 3a XL 則要跟大量大屏幕電話競爭，所以決定只保留 Pixel 4a。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/214882/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4541%2F214882%2F1%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1UwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=04835fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/214882/1/</a>"},{"pid":"018fb2aa5aa12d25e3271b45f645489896f52080","tid":1812401,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3a XL 好用喎"},{"pid":"244935c98397d567ac350b9d65083becbf72dd8a","tid":1812401,"uid":89514,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5de7a66a8fe2acde2ce06473d7e15e859d8b7447","tid":1812401,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"018fb2aa5aa12d25e3271b45f645489896f52080","tid":1812401,"u